<template lang="pug">
.svg-icon(v-if="icon"
          v-html="icon")
</template>
<script>

export default {
  props: {
    path:{
      type: String,
      default: ''
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    console.log(this.icon);
  },
  computed: {
    icon() {
      return require(this.path)
    }
  }
}
</script>
